# 從頭再嚟
(pos:成語/慣用語)
<explanation>
yue:重新開始；由頭再試一次
eng:start over; begin again
<eg>
yue:呢次考試失敗咗，唔好氣餒，我哋可以從頭再嚟。 (ni1 ci3 ko2 si6 sat1 baai3 zo2, m4 hou2 hei3 neoi5, ngo5 dei6 ho2 ji5 cong4 tau4 zoi6 lei4.)
eng:You failed this exam, but don't be discouraged; we can start over.

yue:個計劃行唔通，我哋要從頭再嚟過。 (go3 gai3 faat6 haang4 m4 tung1, ngo5 dei6 jiu3 cong4 tau4 zoi6 lei4 gwo3.)
eng:The plan didn't work, so we need to start from scratch. [end of text]


